title: Weighing Technology
description: OPC 40200: An OPC UA information model for the communication of weighing systems. Main scope is to transport condition data of a weighing instruments vertically into higher level manufacturing systems (MES; etc.) for information and diagnostic purposes and to set information parameters regarding the weighing process (e.g. tare weight, offsets).
